# React Component Conventions

## Component structure

- Functional components only — no class components.
- Page components (`app/**/page.tsx`): use `export default function`.
- Feature components: named exports preferred, registered in the feature's `index.ts` barrel.
- Add `"use client"` directive at the top of any component using hooks, state, or event handlers.

## Next.js primitives

- Use `next/image` (`<Image>`) instead of `<img>`. Set `unoptimized` for data URLs.
- Use `next/link` (`<Link>`) for internal navigation instead of `<a>`.

## Dark theme (globals.css tokens)

All colors come from CSS variables — never hardcode hex values:

| Token | Variable | Use as |
|-------|----------|--------|
| background | `#0a0a0f` | `bg-background` |
| surface | `#12121a` | `bg-surface` |
| surface-light | `#1a1a2e` | `bg-surface-light` |
| border | `#2a2a3e` | `border-border` |
| foreground | `#e8e8f0` | `text-foreground` |
| muted | `#8888a0` | `text-muted` |
| primary | `#6366f1` | `bg-primary`, `text-primary` |
| accent | `#a78bfa` | `text-accent` |
| danger | `#ef4444` | `text-danger` |
| star | `#fbbf24` | `text-star` |

## Styling

- Tailwind utility classes only — no inline `style` attributes.
- No hardcoded color hex values in JSX.

## File placement

- Feature components: `src/features/<feature>/components/` and export from `src/features/<feature>/index.ts`.
- Shared/layout components: `src/components/` and export from `src/components/index.ts`.
